snippet.title: THIS CHICKEN IS GONNA GET DEEP FRIED! | One Way Ticket: Episode 1 | [ALL ENDINGS]
snippet.description:
THIS CHICKEN IS GONNA GET DEEP FRIED! | One Way Ticket: Episode 1 | [ALL ENDINGS]

We're back in my favorite horror genre, cooking/retail! Come see if we can solve all of the mysteries of Chubby's Chicken as we play One Way Ticket: Episode 1, Like a sitting cluck! This episode revolves around an evening shift manager closing a fast-food chicken restaurant by himself.
